name: 专属契约
content: 要亲吻 多少滴眼泪
牵你手 才会更体贴
要穿越 多少次人海
想做你 沉默的后卫
想发光 如果你怕黑
每个瞬间 爱奉陪永远
Baby let me love you more
Baby let me show you more
Don't give up Never never give up
Don't give up Never never give up
想变成 山顶那颗星
因为要 住进你眼睛
保护你 公主的梦境
听见你 喊我的姓名
世界再大 都朝你奔袭
去签名 下一站风景
Baby let me love you more
Baby let me show you more
Don't give up Never never give up
Don't give up Never never give up
Don't give up Never never give up
Don't give up Never never give up
